      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's more than just \"maybe\" though. it's specific. like yesterday, the way the starlings were grouping together in that rapid pulsing motion... it was exactly what happens right before the front moves in. and i'm not just seeing it, i'm actually picking up on the rhythm of it. it's like a language. it's almost like my brain is syncing up with their patterns. doesn't it feel like there's a deeper level to how they coordinate that we usually just ignore?",
